cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is about multi-document summarization, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a discriminative reranking technique that involves machine learning, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper also involves optimization techniques, which could make cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a possible sub-category.
